Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:44.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}心中卻深知再也沒有「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}人生地疏的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:51.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}我們在此相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:58.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}不知何時 微風在身邊刮起
