Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會夢見到  只出現在夢裡的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一望無垠的蔚藍世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐白色的紙飛機翱翔著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  大家出於善意而來騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們盡情地做自己力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複了不知多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只為了完成一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽後拍的那張照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的表情都很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那是最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首場比賽竟然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明差一點就能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪某個笨蛋被人給三振出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為你防守時摔倒的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為腳掌心被刺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你要光著腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫忙準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  就得這樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼要開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同學主辦的烤薄餅派對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫  用那邊的碗把雞蛋和麵粉混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  交給我的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙霧瀰漫的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子呢  庫公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  幹勁十足的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters全體成員聚在一起舉行派對還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  我們來負責裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  瞭解了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去把這個給裝上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我則是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製造煙霧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然連乾冰都準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把飲料給帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位  已經準備妥當了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了一個什麼忙都不幫的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  鈴醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等會兒跳跳糖讓你吃個夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多準備OK了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宴會開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  小毬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次的棒球比賽真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為充滿了笑容和幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一回烤薄餅派對開始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多吃點  多喝點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多唱點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉YEAHYEAH  肌肉YEAHYEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一幫傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來  快請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會做許許多多出來  所以請放開肚子吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個由小葉子收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了  這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情破餅切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮澤同學原來是那種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是從屋頂跳下來的時候腦子摔壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為充滿槽點  意味深長的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有一手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  我還是第一次吃你親手做的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著做下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家喜歡塗什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆成山的樹莓最棒了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推薦杏子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋黃醬甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蘊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蘊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這個是把剛才所說的東西全混在一起的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  為什麼要由我來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤薄餅派對大獲成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子快撐破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的…勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像話  我還能接著吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是…好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派對的結束總會讓人有點傷感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}要等麵粉變硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}變硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想  今後大家能這樣聚在一起的機會也不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論是什麼故事都會迎來結局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會變得不能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮人在道別之後消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  你多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶  小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷唯湖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人反胃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  為什麼這麼討厭來谷同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人譏笑了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我說成是個一無是處的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上的大家都變得看不起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就這麼算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與過去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一成不變的時光在慢慢流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會如此不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問一下  今天是幾號來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是寫著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是二十號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}沒關係  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這雨還真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是繼續這樣下去  明天也沒法練習棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞播報完畢  下面是六月二十日的天氣預報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到午後六點為止  降水機率達70%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事了  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能怎樣  庫特公的書包裡被塞進了這麼多圖釘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子裡好像也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No problem的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小庫  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也隱瞞了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰有犯人的線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她那表情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  做那種事情也沒有意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然心軟了  睦實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別把這事捅出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把圖釘放入庫特的書包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕爛小毬同學的筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道耶  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你有我們做的證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據呢  證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把圖釘放到能美的書包裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好樣的好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼挑能美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們討厭的不是來谷同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她本人嘗點苦頭是沒有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要對她身邊的人下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們知道跟來谷親近是沒有好下場的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把來谷孤立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  她能找到同伴也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是一個怎麼捉弄都無動於衷的怪物機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是你們想要的所謂證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼需要解釋的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等  這…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「啊  等等  這…」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪國的語言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑我所知道的七國語言之一說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剛剛的片段得知主犯有兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一人只是剛好在場  並不是實行犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不加以制止而選擇袖手旁觀也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  該如何對付你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是剛剛聽到的那一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆把陰謀從頭到尾放到全校廣播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竊聽嗎  你這個罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不覺得你們還有值得保護的人權
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會放過你  你這人的存在就是我的眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你消失了  去年的班級就能唯我是從了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  有種你就試試去廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我就讓你們這幫人統統完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們關係不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有無數個把你們搞死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你們的友誼之環粉碎之前我是不會罷手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想變成那樣的話就老老實實地說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我明白了  請住手吧高宮同學」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓你的臉蛋嚐嚐剛才這腳的滋味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無非就是變得再也無法照鏡子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我感覺自己就算成為殺人犯也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不指望能讓你們謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你們要是真的感受到了恐懼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就別再跟我扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎  人渣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於你  我就當作什麼都沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要再跟我扯上關係了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大致猜到發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷  理樹  這兒就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當事人還是別在這兒比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒分出勝負呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠你一個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是不想把我們牽扯進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名什麼的對我來說根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  同伴們的關懷還是得好好接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到這麼生氣的來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  原來我也會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直覺得自己沒有任何感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換言之就是像機器人一般的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論別人對我做什麼  我都能夠承受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來谷同學才不是什麼機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很在乎大家  所以才會那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就證明你也是性情中人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性情…中人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論面對什麼  內心都沒有絲毫動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在成為你們的同伴之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是廣播室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是廣播委員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…以前來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是廣播委員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也有過相同的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一直留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  突然就降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗜睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像往常一樣  突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切斷了我與這個世界的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣播室裡有雨水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  那時也在下雨
